            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昶昕(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:8438:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8438\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8438-TW</a>)近5分K漲速5.71%，28日11:31報70.3元，成交1,248張，今日漲幅為4.3％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昶昕(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:8438:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8438\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8438-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲8.71%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-114 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-53 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+154 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-215 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,178 張</li> <li>融券增減：+5 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
